	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yaulp is a wasted spell fer a cleric.&nbsp;&nbsp;Don't bother meming that specially if yer in a group.<br><br>Root is a clerics best friend.  Ye aggroed ya don't really need to call a tank over.  Just back up root it and then go back to healin.<br><br>Kasparov.<br>Trueborn of Brell-Serelis<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
